<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Hukdampa chu a pui tau,
 Kalvari ah, Kalvari ah;
 Kraws giktak chu a putsak ui,
 Chau mahmah in a pukpiha;
 Enun, Pathien Belam No chun, (2)
 Khawvel gitlohna A puotai (2)

[V2]
 2. Migilote'n a khaikang ui,
 Kalvari ah Kalvari ah.
 Muhsitna lukhuk khuksak in.
 Thing hansie dawlah A maua;
 Tuchan hinle ka gitlohna,
 Ling sangin a sun na zaw sek (2)

[V3]
 3. Nawpna tuipi chim ka dawn tai,
 Kalvari tanga luong dawkchu;
 Van Lallukhuk ka khuk theihna'n,
 Aman linglukhuk a na khui;
 Ei hehpih zie ka genthei puoi,
 Lalpa, hun chawian zing ingka (2)

[V4]
 4. Ka hukdampa chu a thi tai,
 Kalvari ah, Kalvari ah;
 A thawkna haw chu ka hetin,
 Ka gitloh mei zing a kithiel,
 &quot;Thisan lunin ka hun tan tai,
 Gitloh suoka pawtin&quot; ei tii, (2)

[V5]
 5. Sana Lallukhuk sang inle,
 A linglukhuk a hawihzaw ie
 Khawvel hawihna pen sang inle
 A niem lai pen le a hawih zawi
 A thuom bukima kithuom chu.
 Bang guol phetin a hawihta dem(2)</lyrics>
<title>Kalvari ah</title>
</song>